Package cse360assign2

Class AddingMachine

  • java.lang.Object
    • cse360assign2.AddingMachine

  • public class AddingMachine
extends java.lang.Object
    Performs basic add and subtract calculations and maintains calculation history accessible through a toString method. This class includes an add and subtract method designed to perform respective calculations on a rolling total. toString allows the user to print a history of performed calculations to console. clear allows the user to reset the calculations to 0.

    Name: Liam McDonald
    Course: CSE 360
    Assignment: 2

    Author:
    Liam McDonald
